io.dazraf.vertx.futures.processors

Interface PeekProcessor<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Function<io.vertx.core.Future<T>,io.vertx.core.Future<T>>, FutureProcessor<T,T>

    public interface PeekProcessor<T>
extends FutureProcessor<T,T>
    A FutureProcessor to examine the state of the chain. Any exceptions thrown by the peek consumer function are ignored.
